<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1285318>
    dc:description "FIGURES 37–39. Cardiacephala erugata. 37, male, lateral view. Abbreviation: plp—Palpus; 38, male, dorsal view; 39, male genitalia, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1285318/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1285352>
    dc:description "FIGURES 93–96. Cardiacephala umbra. 93, female, dorsolateral view; 94, female genitalia, ventral view; 95, male, dorsolateral view; 96, male genitalia, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1285352/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1285304>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–15. Cardiacephala arthritica. 12, female, Costa Rica; 13, Female genitalia with taxonomically significant structures labeled, ventral view. Abbreviations: bc—Bursa copulatrix, pd—Paired spermathecal duct, pds—Paired spermathecal duct stem, ps—Paired spermathecae, sd—Single spermathecal duct, ss—Single spermathecae, vr—Ventral receptacle (...) Abbreviations: ec—Epicephalon, fr—Frontal setae, iv—Inner vertical seta, os—Orbital seta, ov—Outer vertical seta, pc—Paracephalon, po—Postocellar seta, vx—Vertex (…) Abbreviation: s5—Sternite 5." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1285304/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1285308>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20–23. Cardiacephala brevipennis. 20, female, lateral view; 21, female genitalia, ventral view; 22, male, dorsolateral view; 23, male Sternite 5 and genitalia, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1285308/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1285324>
    dc:description "FIGURES 46–49. Cardiacephala lobulosa. 46, female, dorsolateral view; 47, female genitalia, ventral view; 48, male, dorsolateral view; 49, male sternite 5 and genitalia, ventral and lateral view, respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1285324/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1285326>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50–52. Cardiacephala modesta. 50, female, dorsolateral view; 51, female genitalia, ventral view; 52, male sternite 5 and genitalia, ventral and lateral view, respectively." ;
